summary: An ordinance providing for the manner of advertising and receiving bids for bonds of the City of Seattle in amounts of $135,000.00 authorized by Ordinance No. 30820, $345,000.00 authorized by Ordinance No. 30821, $495,000.00, authorized by Ordinance No. 30822, $425,000.00 authorized by Ordinance No. 30328 and $300,000.00 authorized by Ordinance No. 30715.
